## Best Practices

1. **Title Format**: Always use "Page Title | Site Name" format
2. **Description Length**: Keep between 120-160 characters for optimal display
3. **Unique Content**: Each page must have unique title and description
4. **Schema Validation**: Test schema markup using [Google's Rich Results Test](https://search.google.com/test/rich-results)
5. **Canonical URLs**: Use absolute URLs in schema markup
6. **Dynamic Content**: Use `generateMetadata` for pages with dynamic content
7. **Keywords**: Include 3-5 relevant keywords, avoid keyword stuffing

